   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_3_00009"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Rich.
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb34860" type="place">Steindorf</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">am <rs ref="#pmb40374" type="place">Ossiacher</rs></hi><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb651" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Kärnthen</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_3_00008"/><hi rend="pre-print">Gruss aus der <rs ref="#pmb35499" type="place">Liechtensteinklamm</rs>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1898_AS_RBH_3_00008"/>Sie ent<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chuldigen, lieber Richard aber es gibt überhaupt keine andern. Ich wollte
               Ihnen nur<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>agen: lernen Sie radfahren; Sie herzlich grüßen und bemerken, d<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s es<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chön wäre, we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Sie zwi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen <date>23.</date> u <date>26.</date> in
                  <rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein könnten. – Nachrichten erwarte ich in <rs ref="#pmb34014" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Bad Gastein, Villa Wassing</hi></rs>.</p><closer>Ihr <signed>Arth</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
